      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this exemplary vehicle, a specimen of automotive preservation that transcends the standard pre-owned market. This motorcar has been maintained to a rigorous standard, presenting in pristine aesthetic and mechanical condition. The exterior retains a showroom-level finish, while the interior cabin reflects meticulous care, free from any signs of wear. Undergoing a comprehensive technical appraisal, this vehicle offers an unrivaled driving experience for the most discerning professional. It represents a rare opportunity to acquire a high-performance asset in its most desirable state.",
